headline: Why Best Buy (BBY) Stock Is Up Today
summary: Shares of electronics retailer Best Buy (NYSE:BBY) jumped 8.8% in the afternoon session after investors reacted positively to a softer U.S. tone on trade with China, which eased worries about potential tariffs that could impact the retailer.
